{"tid":581369,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"廣深高鐵癱瘓：虎門封站疏客　「免費巴」竟收費","createTime":"2018-03-05T09:47:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-14T23:45:26.000Z","uid":39464,"like":41,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"152c352490355c47ff5bc6c69dafd783cdedb709","tid":581369,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T09:47:56.000Z","msg":"一場設施故障，導致廣深港高鐵廣州南至虎門段周一（5日）由上午7時許開始至下午2時後，依然處於癱瘓狀態。東莞虎門高鐵站更實施封站，阻止乘客再逼進站內。據指現場有人聲稱有免費旅遊巴疏導受影響的旅客，但有乘客卻稱，上車後遭人索取車費，而且要求提供收據更被拒絕。 <br />\n<br />\n內地媒體報道，東莞虎門高鐵站於中午「截人」，在場警員及工作人員封鎖站內的各入口，阻止乘客再迫入站內；另站內的售票處及候車月台都擠滿了受阻滯留的乘客，由於現場太多人聚集，有乘客既無法離開，也無法退票，怨聲四起。 <br />\n<br />\n在場工作人員稱，下午3時前都不會有列車經停該站，原因不明。據指現場有人向旅客表示，旅客可轉搭車輛，而且是免費的，「但後來上車的乘客每人被收取50元人民幣（約62港元）車費」，並拒絕提供相關收據。 <br />\n<br />\n網傳短片及照片所見，東莞虎門高鐵站內迫滿滯留乘客，而售票處則排起了長長的退票隊伍；站外有大批警員戒備，而工作人員則架起重重「鐵馬」，指示乘客排隊輪候轉移旅遊巴。另有照片可以看到，旅遊巴內有一名大媽對乘客兇神惡煞，手上更拿住大疊的百元鈔票，疑趁火打劫向乘客索取費用，惟其身份是否高鐵方面的工作人員，還是趁亂詐騙，則有待進一步確認。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180305/photo/bkncn-20180305144641545-0305_05011_001_01p.jpg?20180305160308\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180305%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20180305144641545-0305_05011_001_01p.jpg%3F20180305160308&h=75958028&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大批警員到虎門站戒備（左圖）；疑向乘客收費的大媽（右圖），兇神惡煞地喝罵，且其手上拿有大疊百元鈔票。（網上圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180305/photo/bkncn-20180305144641545-0305_05011_001_02p.jpg?20180305160308\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180305%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20180305144641545-0305_05011_001_02p.jpg%3F20180305160308&h=2d8b2900&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n獲安排坐上旅遊巴的乘客拍下車外的混亂場面。（網上圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180305/photo/bkncn-20180305144641545-0305_05011_001_03p.jpg?20180305160308\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180305%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20180305144641545-0305_05011_001_03p.jpg%3F20180305160308&h=acae4c27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180305/photo/bkncn-20180305144641545-0305_05011_001_04p.jpg?20180305160308\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180305%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20180305144641545-0305_05011_001_04p.jpg%3F20180305160308&h=9db67b50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180305/photo/bkncn-20180305144641545-0305_05011_001_05p.jpg?20180305160308\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180305%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20180305144641545-0305_05011_001_05p.jpg%3F20180305160308&h=1c931e77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n站內電子牌上顯示多班列車延誤的訊息。（網上圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180305/bkncn-20180305144641545-0305_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180305%2Fbkncn-20180305144641545-0305_05011_001.html&d=mR%2Fc%2Bzps6cEDNrZ8EtMDxeargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=f9b5623e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180305/bkncn-20180305144641545-0305_05011_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"f7b90d41866a77461bd7ac57b11e871de2366d45","tid":581369,"uid":122,"like":34,"dislike":1,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T09:50:00.000Z","msg":"中國特色免費巴呀 親"},{"pid":"d855f8d58e61de0da49d72a33deb45bc34f25537","tid":581369,"uid":73262,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T09:51:28.000Z","msg":"所以話呢  大陸景色永遠都咁壯觀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8db720293165580384b1b827e085bc17ae1d9c14","tid":581369,"uid":156363,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T09:53:31.000Z","msg":"免費上車，但冇話過開車免費喎！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa377ef90073439933771ab9eb6aff1d42eb6b91","tid":581369,"uid":42188,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"